title: Dakine Duel Pack 26L
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Duel Pack 26L in Fusion.
Duel Pack features: 
- Padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 14" laptops
- Skateboard carry straps
- Insulated cooler pocket
- Organizer pocket
- Fleece lined sunglass pocket
- Mesh side pockets
- Adjustable sternum strap
